
!IMPORTANT! You need UHD version 3.9.7 in order to compile and run this program.
            Be sure to install and link this version before proceeding.


To compile the program, prepare the Makefile and then build it with make.
These are the commands to run for compiling it:

    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make

Run the program with:

    $ ./btsniffer 

To see all available options, run:

    $ ./btsniffer --help

